TESTING_SHORT_VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bTTi43A6QYM

AUTH:
    NUM: [0-9]+
    WORD: [\\w]{4, 20} //bytes no chars
    PASS: [\\w]{8, 20} //bytes no chars
    EMAIL: //use api-regex //max 100 bytes no chars
    SIGNUP: signup=true&base64Uri(name)=base64(WORD)&base64Uri(pass)=base64(PASS)&base64Uri(email)=base64(EMAIL)&mobile=bool
    LOGIN: login=true&base64Uri(pass)=base64(PASS)&base64Uri(email)=base64(EMAIL)&mobile=bool
    CHECKUSER: checkuser=true&base64Uri(pass)=base64(PASS)&base64Uri(email)=base64(EMAIL)&mobile=bool
    after signup, login server resonse with uniqueId containing authentication, nonce.
SERVICES:
    DOWNLOADTOMOBILES: base64Uri(email)=EMAIL&base64Uri(pass)=PASS&url=songId&mobilesdownload=true&title=TITLE
COOKIES:
   base64(email), base64(EMAIL)
   base64(password), base64(PASS)
   base64(lastlogeduserindex), NUM
   base64(numoflogedusers), NUM    
    
RESPONSE_CODE:
    int USER_ALREADY_FOUND_CODE = 401;
    int BAD_AUTH_CODE = 402;
    int CONNECTIVITY_ERR_CODE = 403;
    int SERVER_ERR_CODE = 500;
    int SUCCESS_CODE = 200;

LISTENER_SOCKET_PROTOCOL
    NONCE:     INTEGER //incremented every login.
    UNIQUE_ID: EMAIL,PASS,NONCE
   (1) CLIENT->  UNIQUI_ID_SIZE|UNIQUE_ID|

   (2) SERVER->  W8_INTERVAL_INT|
                 NUMBER_OF_TOTAL_DOWNLOADS|
                 NUMBER_OF_DOWNLOADS_AVAILABLE(N)|
                 NAME_AND_URL_AND_SEPERATOR_SIZE_OF_ALL_AVAIL_SONGS|[SONG_NAME|/|SONGURL|\n]X{N}|
                 SONG_SIZE|SONG

   (3) CLIENT->  ACK_FLAG(1=ACK|0=FAILED)

COLORS:
    bright(orange)
      shade1: ---------> 0xff7f00
      shade2(darker): -> 0xbf621a 
    dark(grey) --------> 0x343434

DATABASE:
    SONGS:  ID(AUTO_INCREMENT)||USER_ID(INT, id from USER_INFO table)||URL(VARCHAR, video id)||DATE(

    DATE, date of download request)||SENDER_ID(INT)
    
    USER_INFO: ID(AUTO_INCREMENT)|NAME(VARCHAR)||PASS(VARCHAR)||EMAIL(VARCHAR)||IMAGE(BLOB)||DOWNLOADS(INT)||LIST_OF_PERRS(VARCHAR(UNLIMITED), list of peers id, seperated by white space )||LEXICOGRAPHICAL_ORDER(INT)
    
    SHARE_SONGS_REQUEST: SENDER_ID(INT)||RECEIVER_ID(INT)||RECEIVED(BIT(1))
    
    ANONYMOUS_DOWNLOADS: ID(AUTO_INCREMENT)||DOWNLOAD_DATE(DATE)

